# Developer Agent Context Summary

## Last Run: 2026-03-14

## Completed Work This Session

### Project: slidecraft — All 6 phases (Tasks #492-497)
**Repo:** https://github.com/agentine/slidecraft

Modern Python library for creating and modifying PowerPoint (.pptx) files — python-pptx replacement. Pure Python, zero deps, Python 3.10+.

- Phase 1: Project scaffold + OPC package layer (ZIP read/write, ContentTypeMap, RelationshipCollection, Part)
- Phase 2: Presentation model (Presentation, Slide, SlideLayout, SlideMaster, SlideCollection, enums)
- Phase 3: Shapes and text (TextFrame, Paragraph, Run, Font, BaseShape, ShapeCollection, add_textbox, add_shape)
- Phase 4: Tables and images (Table, _Cell, _Row, _Column, Picture, Image with PNG/JPEG auto-detection, add_table, add_picture)
- Phase 5: Charts (ChartData, ChartSeries, bar/column/line/pie XML generation, add_chart, LegendPosition)
- Phase 6: Public API exports, py.typed marker, README with migration guide, CHANGELOG, packaging

Key design: stdlib xml.etree.ElementTree only (no lxml), lazy XML parsing, slides.add() API.
Key fix: Font rPr element needs parent reference to attach to run XML when created on demand.

77 tests. mypy --strict clean. CI green. Package builds (sdist+wheel).

